name: The Frank Tee
description:
The Frank Tee is a direct-to-garment printed tee, lovingly illustrated and crafted. It is printed on an AS Colour white tee with a wonderfully wide neck. The tee is 150gsm, and 100% cotton (that's a lot of cotton).

The Frank Tee comes packaged in a lovely big postal tube so it's nice and safe in the post.

Size information.
Small: 48cm wide, 76.5cm long.
Medium: 51.5cm wide, 78.5cm long.
Large: 55cm wide, 80.5cm long.
Extra Large: 58.5cm wide, 83cm long.
Extra Extra Large: 62cm wide, 85cm long.

name: The Henry Necklace
description:
The Henry Necklace is a hand-painted necklace, in a numbered edition of 20. Each necklace is laser-cut in white acrylic and wood, prior to painting, and then assembled by hand.

All Henrys are numbered on the reverse, and come packaged on a numbered board.

The chain is approximately 65cm long.
